- List partitions
(Windows Management Instrumentation)
wmic logicaldisk get name
wmic logicaldisk get caption
wmic logicaldisk get deviceid, volumename, description

fsutil fsinfo drives

diskpart
list volume

powershell
get-psdrive -psprovider filesystem


